            "text": " **Lemma 4.** Let  $(W_t)_t$  be Wulff-shape perturbations of a given convex body K, with respect to  $(\\Omega, f)$ . Then for  $S_K$ -almost every  $u \\in \\mathbb{S}^{n-1}$ :",
