            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": " *Proof.* First, recall that, for all  $u \\in \\mathbb{S}^{n-1}$ , the map  $(t \\mapsto h_{W_t}(u))$  is concave on  $]t_0, +\\infty[$ , where  $t_0 = t_0(K, \\Omega, f) = \\inf\\{t \\in \\mathbb{R} : |W_t|_n > 0\\}.",
