            "text": " As this holds for any  $u \\in \\Omega$ , one concludes that  $(1 - \\lambda)W_{t_1} + \\lambda W_{t_2} \\subset W_{t_{\\lambda}}$ , from which concavity (on the domain  $]t_0, +\\infty[$ ) of  $(t \\mapsto h_{W_t}(u))$ , for any fixed  $u \\in \\mathbb{S}^{n-1}$ , readily follows.",
